1 C. Rules promulgated by Service Oklahoma under the provisions
2 of subsection B of this section shall require an applicant for the
3 license to have three (3) years of verifiable commercial driving
4 experience within ten (10) years of the application date or three
5 (3) years of verifiable experience as an instructor at a commercial
6 driver training school within ten (10) years of the application
7 date.
8 SECTION 2. It being immediately necessary for the preservation
9 of the public peace, health or safety, an emergency is hereby
10 declared to exist, by reason whereof this act shall take effect and
11 be in full force from and after its passage and approval.
